{"tid":1448723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被黑警拉到好撚爽？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:57.000Z","uid":262289,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3278820517a920bdb95a5ccbe9a9e9d613c33497","tid":1448723,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"根本人多就可以救到人 可以減少被捕率！唔好白白犧牲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠多人就衝過去救人啦 唔通你忍心你隔離個手足就咁冇左？<br />\n你唔救 佢既10年青春可能就會冇左<br />\n<br />\n當人地都冇底線 點解仲要俾條底線自己？就算打返班狗轉頭都無可厚非 <br />\n<br />\n唔好淆班狗！！！人多既時候記得去救人！手足捉一個少一個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n香港加油 唔好俾極權大到我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beceac1879dfb5ed038d38de9d2f942504d5838","tid":1448723,"uid":134178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3278820517a920bdb95a5ccbe9a9e9d613c33497","tid":1448723,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"根本人多就可以救到人 可以減少被捕率！唔好白白犧牲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠多人就衝過去救人啦 唔通你忍心你隔離個手足就咁冇左？<br />\n你唔救 佢既10年青春可能就會冇左<br />\n<br />\n當人地都冇底線 點解仲要俾條底線自己？就算打返班狗轉頭都無可厚非 <br />\n<br />\n唔好淆班狗！！！人多既時候記得去救人！手足捉一個少一個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n香港加油 唔好俾極權大到我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"手足唔該幫幫手<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812 1PM起，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，唔係我們既責任，係因為機場唔夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n不要說推<br />\n試著說 812 機場見"},{"pid":"8147b1f214a7f15d390cb5f67c8d21d72eb38136","tid":1448723,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />救人啊！"},{"pid":"29b019a55665b6bd80f69fe40609af930b38355a","tid":1448723,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=f695bc1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n去信Nonlethal Technologies投訴香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447918</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1604dc0a13261d8747e4405307ce035c013d8870","tid":1448723,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n有片見到其實啲狗唔係一堆衝<br />\n係兩三個圍一個<br />\n手足肯救其實救到"},{"pid":"19441c05947bd823f2eeed3d0a3eb3426f92f8c8","tid":1448723,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca75c0b3b2f34b2552f01602bbc7c78f92ea44a2","tid":1448723,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"你地依家唔知邊d人需要落台，甚至送上國際法庭咩？<br />\n<br />\n大家都知呀，咁要獨立調查委員咩用呀？<br />\n<br />\n散水咋！"},{"pid":"50d784a4941a08cb44f1c98ff1792fa3a7ed97ed","tid":1448723,"uid":63263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d49d13dac31f99cecb90e6d10916a6dd9fb338","tid":1448723,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1604dc0a13261d8747e4405307ce035c013d8870","tid":1448723,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n有片見到其實啲狗唔係一堆衝<br />\n係兩三個圍一個<br />\n手足肯救其實救到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"只要幾個圍佢地 基本上一定救到人！<br />\n主要唔好淆班狗！主動性返轉頭救人！"},{"pid":"84ed0b19839ed16fd3e690acad1698c9654c0a56","tid":1448723,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場</span>